      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so quiet here. i walk into the kitchen and i keep expecting to hear him making coffee or just... something. but there's nothing. it feels like i'm just a ghost wandering around a house that doesn't belong to me anymore. i don't even know why i bother waking up just to sit in this silence. it feels like the world just stopped, but everyone else kept going. it's not right.",
